rows.label: qst001603_msg0001
rows.name:
Thanks. Sorry for bothering
you so many times.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0002
rows.name: Now, let's try out the new menu.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0003
rows.name:
I'd like you to taste-test it again,
so please wait just a moment.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0006
rows.name: See? This one's not bad either, right?

rows.label: qst001603_msg0007
rows.name:
Thanks to your help, the
new menu is complete.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0008
rows.name: Let me give you your reward.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0009
rows.name:
After all your hard work, just giving
you money seems a bit dull, so I came
up with a new recipe for you.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0010
rows.name: I call it the True Hero Adel Grill!

rows.label: qst001603_msg0011
rows.name:
It's a no-expense-spared dish,
but it should be the most delicious
food in all of Superbia.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0012
rows.name:
If there's a cook among
you, please try making it.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0014
rows.name:
No, you're the one who
helped me out. See you!
